Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and now I will just leave you to it
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.92,0:09:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and come back here in 5 or 10 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.54,0:09:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,once you are ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.87,0:09:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, here we are back
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.19,0:09:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and I hope that it wasn't too much of a challenge for you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.03,0:09:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so that I wasn't too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.60,0:09:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So hopefully you got
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.67,0:09:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to practice your skills a little bit more
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and so now in case you have any doubts
