Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.17,0:09:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so each page should only have one h1
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.01,0:09:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and so if we then have multiple articles,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.37,0:10:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,then each of them should just be an h2.
