Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.67,0:10:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I could have just copied this from the demo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.45,0:10:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.72,0:10:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So img
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and now I will actually go ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.79,0:10:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and copy this URL here
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.45,0:10:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,in the editor view.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.18,0:10:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.10,0:10:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then the alt text is,
