Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.93,0:10:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This should be enough like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.22,0:10:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And then the height
