Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.93,0:11:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.26,0:11:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here is our image.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.34,0:11:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.24,0:11:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now let's go back here
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.80,0:11:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and actually copy all of this content.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.32,0:11:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.35,0:11:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then we can just, after that,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.72,0:11:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,wrap everything into its own element.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.41,0:11:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So here we have the price.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.96,0:11:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I will keep using a paragraph for each
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.73,0:11:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,of these elements,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.10,0:11:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so for each of the text elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.40,0:11:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then we have free shipping.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.13,0:11:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.31,0:11:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And you see that CodePen
