Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that's quite helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.03,0:11:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then here there's another paragraph.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.51,0:12:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.75,0:12:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So we are getting our content formatted,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.93,0:12:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,except, of course, for all the content
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that is not inside any element.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.61,0:12:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So remember how I mentioned that HTML doesn't care
