Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.98,0:12:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So like line breaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.45,0:12:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is just in the same line
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.40,0:12:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and so that's why we need to structure our content
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.15,0:12:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,in a logical way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.41,0:12:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, here we have that anchor element.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.17,0:12:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And actually, I didn't really tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.00,0:12:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,where this link should point to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.37,0:12:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you could have just created an empty link
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.47,0:12:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,like this basically,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.47,0:12:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,or you could have linked the Converse website.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.66,0:12:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So let me just grab that link.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.28,0:12:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So converse.com probably
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.67,0:12:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm doing it like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.51,0:12:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You will see in a moment why.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.89,0:13:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And the reason is because we actually need this https://.
