Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.65,0:13:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is not necessary here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.61,0:13:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And now here let's close this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.75,0:13:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And here, of course, we do not just want this symbol
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.49,0:13:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,because this is not really correct,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so instead, we want that HTML entity
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that you hopefully used.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.08,0:13:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that is the right arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.56,0:13:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the abbreviation here,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.93,0:13:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,for r stands for right
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.92,0:13:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and then arr for arrow
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.80,0:13:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and so indeed, this is the result that we got.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.35,0:13:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So we have all of this part.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.69,0:13:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now let's take care of this list here
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.56,0:13:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and this heading.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.96,0:13:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And finally then also this button.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.52,0:13:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I have an h2 already up here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.85,0:14:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so for this one, I'm using an h3 now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.31,0:14:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H3.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And closing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.07,0:14:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.90,0:14:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And now remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.04,0:14:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,in order to create a list, which is what we want here,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.91,0:14:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so a bullet-pointed list,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.73,0:14:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we use the unordered element
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,or actually, the unordered list element.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.02,0:14:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And now we just wrap all
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.33,0:14:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,of these into one li element, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I hope that at this point,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you already know these elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.01,0:14:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you have practiced a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.74,0:14:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and so I'm sure
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that this is getting a lot more easy for you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.23,0:14:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just remove this dot here
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.35,0:14:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and we are almost done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.72,0:14:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So all we need now is that button in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.27,0:15:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so as I showed you before,
