Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.95,0:15:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So add to cart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.95,0:15:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And of course, that button,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.42,0:15:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so clicking that button will not do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.32,0:15:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For that, we would need some JavaScript.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.09,0:15:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But at least it is here visible, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.43,0:15:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And we see here that we have 80 unsaved changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.65,0:15:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So if you want to preserve those changes again,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.31,0:15:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you would have to save the CodePen
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.21,0:15:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and create a free account in order to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.90,0:15:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh and I thought that we were actually done
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.19,0:15:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,with this challenge
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.08,0:15:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but there is one small piece missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.35,0:15:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So this text here in the original is actually bold.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.76,0:15:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the only difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.87,0:15:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that's something that we're missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.61,0:15:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so let's simply wrap this value here,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.49,0:15:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so all this text into a strong element.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.73,0:16:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not string, strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.01,0:16:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And you see now at this point,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.98,0:16:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we didn't close this tag,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.83,0:16:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so this strong element
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.35,0:16:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and so now all the rest
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.89,0:16:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,of the content basically became strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.00,0:16:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So everything is bold now
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.75,0:16:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,because this element never ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.39,0:16:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But, of course, that would be a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.51,0:16:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't even be valid HTML
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.70,0:16:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but the browsers somehow still
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.52,0:16:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,are able to render it somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.17,0:16:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But anyway, with this, we finished this challenge
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.54,0:16:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and actually also the introduction to HTML section.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.86,0:16:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So make sure to review everything
