Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.17,0:17:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and more beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.67,0:17:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that's really, really exciting
